## Additional Terms for Motorcycle Tuning

### Educational Purpose
This software is provided for educational and research purposes in the motorcycle 
tuning community. Users are responsible for understanding and complying with all 
applicable laws and regulations regarding vehicle modifications in their jurisdiction.

### Safety Disclaimer
The authors and contributors of this software are not responsible for any damage 
to motorcycles, ECUs, or other vehicle components that may result from the use 
of this software. Users should:

- Always backup original ECU tunes before making modifications
- Verify tune compatibility with their specific motorcycle
- Understand the risks associated with ECU modifications
- Consider warranty implications of vehicle modifications
- Consult with qualified professionals when in doubt

### Data Sources
All motorcycle specifications and tune data included in this software are sourced 
from publicly available information, official manufacturer specifications, and 
legitimate open-source tuning communities.

### Compliance
Users are solely responsible for ensuring their use of this software complies 
with local laws, regulations, and manufacturer warranty terms. 